			<div class="post post-quote">
				<p class="quote">We are what we pretend to be, so we must be careful about what we pretend to be.</p>
				<p class="source">- Kurt Vonnegut (Born November 11, 1922), Mother Night<p>(Source: <a href="http://www.goodreads.com/work/quotes/1222244" title="goodreads.com">goodreads.com</a>)</p></p>
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
		
			
			
			
				
