			<div class="date">
				<span class="month"><a href="http://joshuastarlight.tumblr.com/post/1476536038/the-realm-of-fairy-story-is-wide-and-deep-and-high">Nov</a></span>
				<span class="day"><a href="http://joshuastarlight.tumblr.com/post/1476536038/the-realm-of-fairy-story-is-wide-and-deep-and-high">3</a></span>
